Standard: Вы открываете глаза в пустом кабинете.
en: You found yourself in an empty classroom.

Standard: За окном глубокая ночь. Слышно потрескивание сверчков.
en: It's deep dark night outside the window. You can hear crackling sound of crickets.

Standard: Как долго я был без сознания?
en: How long was I unconscious?
This place brings back memories.

Standard: Я слышу чей-то голос у себя в голове.
en: I hear someone's voice in my head.
It's all somehow wrong.
How did I get here?
Need to go.
I don't need it.
It seems to remind me of something.

Standard: Кажется, от этого амулета исходит странная энергия.
en: There seems to be a strange energy coming from the amulet.
I don't think it's save to come closer.

Standard: Судя по всему, это сводка по экзорцизму.
en: Apparently, this is a summary of the exorcism.

Standard: Но зачем мне вся эта информация?
en: But why do I need all this information?
Looks like I wasted my time.

Standard: Я без понятия, что я делаю.
en: I have no idea what I'm doing.
Seems like it might work.
Maybe nothing will come of it.

Standard: А я был так близок к разгадке!
en: I was very close to a solution!
I'm finally free.
Thank you for playing!
Did you think there would be something?
Close the game, go take a shower!

Standard: Да я сломал 4ю стену, и что ты мне сделаешь?
en: Yes, I broke the 4th wall, and what will you do to me?
Close unity schizoid.
ok.
